gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 120, Hornets 84
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Hornets, 120-84. Damian Lillard (26 points, eight assists) and Malik Beasley (21 points, seven 3PT) led the Bucks while Giannis Antetokounmpo added 15 points and 15 rebounds. Brandon Miller (16 points, six rebounds) and Nick Richards (16 points, 11 rebounds) led Charlotte in the loss.
